## [Unreleased]

## [1.0.0] - 2024-08-25

### Added
- Initial release of sus
- Functionality for counting and sorting line frequencies
- Support for high/low count and percentage-based output
- Case-sensitive and case-insensitive modes
- Ability to process multiple input files
- Aggregation option for multiple inputs
- Verbose logging option
- Comprehensive test suite and benchmarks

